rows.label: bf10200100_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Wha...?

rows.label: bf10200100_0020
rows.name: Gramps-!

rows.label: bf10200100_0030
rows.name: This place-

rows.label: bf10200100_0040
rows.name: What is the point...?

rows.label: bf10200100_0050
rows.name: Uh, Gramps?

rows.label: bf10200100_0060
rows.name: What is the point of us, really?

rows.label: bf10200100_0070
rows.name: We are born as Blades, then return to our slumber,

rows.label: bf10200100_0080
rows.name: again and again, over countless years...

rows.label: bf10200100_0090
rows.name:
until we become Divine Beasts, to wander
this world for countless more...

rows.label: bf10200100_0100
rows.name: and at the end of it all, we sink into nothingness.

rows.label: bf10200100_0110
rows.name: Have you ever thought about it?

rows.label: bf10200100_0120
rows.name:
What it means to exist for close to an eternity,
with no clear purpose or goal...

rows.label: bf10200100_0130
rows.name: That's-

rows.label: bf10200100_0140
rows.name: Must be nice to be human...

rows.label: bf10200100_0150
rows.name: Living for a limited time,

rows.label: bf10200100_0160
rows.name:
thinking limited thoughts...
it must be so much easier.

rows.label: bf10200100_0170
rows.name: I envy your kind...

rows.label: bf10200100_0180
rows.name: Just tell me, Rex.

rows.label: bf10200100_0190
rows.name: What should I do?

rows.label: bf10200100_0200
rows.name:
Should I be satisfied with drifting around the ocean,
with you on my back?

rows.label: bf10200100_0210
rows.name: Is that all I am to be?

rows.label: bf10200100_0220
rows.name:
I-I don't know how
I'm supposed to answer that!

rows.label: bf10200100_0230
rows.name: Why are you asking me?!

rows.label: bf10200100_0240
rows.name:
You're being strange...
Everyone's acting so strange!
